    <div class="container">
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> November 4, 2024.</p>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
            <p>Visiuun is a digital platform offering various online services, including the Nekobox File Hosting feature. While Visiuun is an unregistered brand, we remain dedicated to responsible handling of data to protect user privacy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Information Collection and Use</h2>
            <p>We only collect data directly related to the operation of our services and do not engage in any form of tracking or data profiling outside of what is specified here.</p>
            
            <h3>A. General Browsing</h3>
            <p>When you browse our website, Visiuun does not collect any personal information. We use only necessary cookies that are essential for the functioning of our system, such as those required for the operation of Nekobox file hosting. No third-party cookies are used on our platform.</p>
            
            <h3>B. Nekobox File Hosting Service</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Stored Files:</strong> Any files you upload to Nekobox are saved on our servers to facilitate access and storage. We do not analyze, track, or scan these files beyond what is technically necessary for storage and retrieval.</li>
                <li><strong>File Access:</strong> Files stored through Nekobox may be accessed by you or individuals you choose to share the file links with. Visiuun does not provide access to these files to any third parties except in cases of legal requirement (see Section 5).</li>
                <li><strong>No Personal Information Collection:</strong> We do not request personal information from you when you upload files to Nekobox, nor do we associate uploaded files with specific users.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. How We Protect Your Information</h2>
            <p>While Visiuun collects minimal data, we take every measure to ensure that any files uploaded to Nekobox remain secure:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Data Security:</strong> Files stored on our servers are protected using industry-standard security measures to prevent unauthorized access.</li>
                <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Only users with a valid file link are able to access files stored on Nekobox. We advise caution when sharing links, as anyone with access to a link can view and download the file.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
            <p>Visiuun uses only essential cookies for the proper functioning of our website. These cookies are strictly necessary for the operation of services like file uploading and retrieval. No third-party cookies are used on our platform.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>5. Legal Compliance</h2>
            <p>While we prioritize user privacy, Visiuun may be required by law to disclose stored information under specific circumstances. Such cases may include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Compliance with legal orders, such as subpoenas or court directives.</li>
                <li>Protection of our rights, property, or safety, or that of our users or others.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>In the event of a legally compelled disclosure, we will seek to limit the information disclosed to what is strictly necessary.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>6. Changes to Our Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>Visiuun reserves the right to update this Privacy Policy as our services or legal obligations evolve. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this page periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your privacy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
